The following people have contributed to the FDC+ Serial Drive Server codebase:

Patrick Linstruth <patrick@deltecent.com>
   Original implementation in C — the upstream reference codebase that
   the TypeScript version was ported from. (Era: pre-2024.)

Joe Toppe <mreppot@gmail.com>
   TypeScript rewrite, web interface (Svelte 5 + Tailwind 4), MCP server,
   GPIO LED status indicators, OpenAPI documentation. (Era: 2024–present.)

The FDC+ Enhanced Floppy Disk Controller hardware itself is by Mike Douglas
(deramp.com). It is referenced here but not part of this codebase.
